Package: matchr
Title: Fast and Reliable Matching of Images
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "David",
           family = "Wachsmuth",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "david.wachsmuth@mcgill.ca",
           comment = c(ORCID = "http://orcid.org/0000-0001-5689-9527"))
Maintainer: David Wachsmuth <david.wachsmuth@mcgill.ca>
Description: Fast and reliable matching of images. It creates unique colour
    signatures for images by finding average colour values for horizontal bands.
    This allows two or more images to be compared to each other using
    correlations of colour values, and the comparisons are insensitive to
    file format, resolution, or compression.
